metadata.name: PAX 3
metadata.description:
PHYTOLITHS AND XENOBLASTS 3

War is a distraction.
Warfare is based 
only on deception.
If you wave a flag, 
you fell into the trap.

In the beginning, 
most people die 
when the banner is black.
If you draw a sword, 
make sure you are winning,
because you are better off dead.

OPUS SOLVERE: 
For the next 20 hands 
have only peace in your head.
